            "reviews": "“Halfway does not mess around when it comes to difficulty. This is an unashamedly hardcore turn-based experience. And that’s a good thing.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://calmdowntom.com/review/halfway-review-pc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Calm Down Tom</a><br><br>“[...]if you’re wanting an enjoyable sci-fi story with your TBS/RPG elements, then Halfway is more than worth the miniscule price being asked for it. I look forward to the sequel (please).”<br>7.5/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://nzgamer.com/reviews/2126/halfway.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >NZGamer</a><br><br>“My tactics insiders' tip for this summer. (German review)”<br>7.5/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.pcgames.de/Halfway-PC-259248/Tests/Test-mit-Video-Taktik-Geheimtipp-mit-Sci-Fi-Szenario-1129889/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >PC Games</a><br>",
